Yo, yo!

1:14:25.195 --> 1:14:27.495
Dude! Dude, you missed the end.

1:14:27.497 --> 1:14:28.863
The prom king got wasted

1:14:28.865 --> 1:14:31.466
and fell of the stage.
It was hilarious.

1:14:31.468 --> 1:14:33.134
Yeah, it's a shame to miss it.

1:14:34.003 --> 1:14:36.771
Oh, yeah? Real shame, huh?

