(GRUNTS)

1:24:24.827 --> 1:24:26.427
PHILIP: Help!

1:24:26.429 --> 1:24:27.728
Richard?

1:24:27.730 --> 1:24:28.796
I heard it.

1:24:36.772 --> 1:24:38.772
