1:24:41.243 --> 1:24:42.576
Quiet.

1:24:42.578 --> 1:24:44.111
Please be quiet.

1:24:44.113 --> 1:24:46.146
That was Philip.
Philip?

1:24:46.849 --> 1:24:48.215
Philip?

1:24:48.217 --> 1:24:49.550
(GASPING)

1:24:53.622 --> 1:24:55.689
