Charlene!
He's in the woods.

1:25:23.752 --> 1:25:25.252
(GASPING)

1:25:35.631 --> 1:25:36.697
CHARLENE: Oh, God.

1:25:37.233 --> 1:25:38.499
(COUGHING)

1:25:40.870 --> 1:25:42.402
Philip!

1:25:49.411 --> 1:25:50.577
RICHARD: Philip?

1:26:02.925 --> 1:26:04.258
Bill?

1:26:26.615 --> 1:26:27.948
I never meant to hurt her.

1:26:34.223 --> 1:26:35.322
No!
No!

1:26:35.324 --> 1:26:36.557
(GUNSHOT)

1:26:41.430 --> 1:26:42.829
MELISSA: I love you, Ronnie.

1:26:45.334 --> 1:26:46.466
I love you, too.

1:26:50.773 --> 1:26:52.372
You don't sound so sure.

1:27:00.416 --> 1:27:01.548
(CLEARS THROAT)

1:27:02.484 --> 1:27:04.251
I love Melissa Moody.

