<i> As adults, we offer</i>
<i> answers without proof.</i>

1:30:17.780 --> 1:30:21.815
<i> I now understand</i>
<i> there isn't any single answer.</i>

1:30:22.885 --> 1:30:24.885
<i> We must all walk our own path,</i>

1:30:25.654 --> 1:30:27.020
<i> and find our own truth.</i>

1:30:29.625 --> 1:30:30.891
<i> But I figure,</i>

1:30:32.027 --> 1:30:33.493
<i> if I go my way,</i>

1:30:34.930 --> 1:30:36.096
